---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { Container } from '../components/layout/Container';
import { Section } from '../components/layout/Section';
import { QualificationForm } from '../components/forms/QualificationForm';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Free AI Readiness Audit - Is Your Account Built for AI Search? | GrowMyAds"
  description="Google search is now AI-powered. Is your account optimized for it? Get a free audit to see if you're ready for AI-driven search and your exact transition roadmap."
>
  <Section background="gray" spacing="xl">
    <Container size="lg">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-yellow-100 border border-yellow-300 rounded-full mb-6">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-yellow-700" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm1-12a1 1 0 10-2 0v4a1 1 0 00.293.707l2.828 2.829a1 1 0 101.415-1.415L11 9.586V6z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-yellow-900 text-sm font-semibold">
            Limited Availability in October
          </span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 leading-tight">
          Is Your Account Built for<br/>AI-Powered Search?
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-gray-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
          Google fundamentally changed how search works in 2024-2025. If your account is still optimized for keyword-based search, you're working against the algorithm.
        </p>

        <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto bg-gradient-to-br from-navy-50 to-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-xl p-8">
          <p class="font-bold text-navy-950 mb-4 text-lg">Your AI Readiness Audit includes:</p>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-left">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-800 font-medium"><strong>Data Quality Assessment:</strong> Is your conversion tracking feeding Google the signals it needs to train its AI? (Most accounts track the wrong things)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-800 font-medium"><strong>Structure Analysis:</strong> Is your account consolidated for AI learning or fragmented using 2019 keyword segmentation tactics?</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-800 font-medium"><strong>AI Training Roadmap:</strong> Your exact path from current state to AI-optimized: data quality → conversion volume → smart bidding → broad match → scale</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-8">Answer 10 questions below → Schedule 30-min strategy call → Get your AI transition roadmap</p>

        <div class="mt-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-600 p-6 rounded-r-lg">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-800 leading-relaxed">
              <strong class="text-blue-900">Note:</strong> This audit helps us both determine if we're a good fit. Not every business is ready for the AI transition—and that's okay. We'll be honest about whether we can help.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8 md:p-12">
        <QualificationForm client:load />
      </div>

      {/* Trust Badges */}
      <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4 font-medium">100+ accounts transitioned to AI-first strategy</p>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-6 sm:gap-8 text-sm">
          <div class="text-gray-600 font-semibold">Google Partner</div>
          <div class="text-gray-600 font-semibold">•</div>
          <div class="text-gray-600 font-semibold">No pressure, just honest analysis</div>
          <div class="text-gray-600 font-semibold">•</div>
          <div class="text-gray-600 font-semibold">Education-focused</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </Section>
</BaseLayout>
